      "writtenOn": "2018-08-24T17:20:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is a misunderstanding on my part.  My intent was to look in the same directory as the system images (e.g. $ANDROID_SDK_ROOT/system-images/android-28/google_apis/x86_64/VerifiedBootParams.textproto)\n\nI\u0027m not sure what API call should be used to get this although it seems like adding a method to android/android-emu/android/avd/info.h would follow an existing pattern.  Since info.h methods require a AvdInfo* object, it might be best to change this API to take a path and leave the path finding to the caller (e.g. main) who has a AvdInfo* object on-hand.  I\u0027ll make the change but please me know if you have other suggestions.",
      "parentUuid": "6fd138c2_ca771449",
      "range": {
